## Rail deployment

### Railway CLI Method (Preferred)
requires the user to login in the run:
```bash
railway login --service mwd-backend --path backend
# or from the project root
railway up --service mwd-backend -d
```

### Via GitHub Integration
```bash
# After linking GitHub, push to trigger auto-deploy
git push origin main
```

### Required Environment Variables

For local development:
```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://mwd-backend-production.up.railway.app
```

For Railway service variables:
```bash
MWD_CORS_ORIGINS=*
MWD_LOG_LEVEL=info
```

